des: "Refreshing and delicious combination of frozen raspberries, orange juice, and mint, with a kick."
ins: Blend raspberries, tequila, orange juice, lemon juice, orange liqueur, superfine sugar, and mint leaves in a blender until smooth. Add ice cubes individually, crushing each one before adding the next. Pour into chilled cocktail glasses to serve.
